      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "If one wants line by line debugging, `gdb` or `lldb` is probably the most simplest way to do this. Just use `./configure --enable-debug` and run `gdb src/bitcoind`.\r\n\r\nUsing Qt Creator's IDE is also an effective how to do line-by-line debugging (more GUIish then gdb) including interactive variable inspection, etc.",
